text: Bergnäset is a locality situated in Luleå Municipality, Norrbotten County, Sweden with 3,648 inhabitants in 2010. The Bergnäs Bridge linking Bergnäset with central Luleå. == References == ==External links== *Bergnäset at Luleå Municipality Category:Populated places in Luleå Municipality Category:Norrbotten
